me":"2020-04-25T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"2047"},{"pid":"1239dde8816389a5c1bf44f2f41748a53e1285db","tid":1988090,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66271dbc4491277ef3382587b33ce6409834b460","tid":1988090,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a736c21f8dad220e8e0659d77f95b77c31d008d","tid":1988090,"uid":221650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"用黎買樓最安全"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:14:07.000Z","msg":"2047"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"Ww3"},{"pid":"f5eaebc3c496416eb33d5d38f28dc219352d2185","tid":1988090,"uid":255333,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"如果真係要買正股收息，可考慮用期權short put，入到會平啲，入唔到當收高息，相反出貨就用short call，好多退休人士夠本錢接貨會咁玩，假設月頭等價做short，一般short到一至兩轉(put或call)已經好過收一年股息，而指數ETF如2800, 2828, 2822亦相對穩陣<br />\n<br />\n當然也有坐貨風險，但既然原本都諗住買嚟收息，風險唔會因為short期權而大咗，最緊要係做covered short，即係有足夠本錢接貨(short put)，或有足夠股票出貨(short call)<br />\n<br />\n過常係搏隻股短期升值驚等唔切至會直接買股"},{"pid":"f70f5c431265b6310ba664fc6c29721f710dbd3d","tid":1988090,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee1e98077db2745e6c411a1f0b8a3d140dca71fa","tid":1988090,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb22e5502aaf0347e50a0825f90d43d270bec2e2","tid":1988090,"uid":42445,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"買年金，重點係食埋生果金同長生津，<br />\n<br />\n得閒渣更的士，中生產生活！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"生果金 同 長生津 係兩個只可拎一個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:44:20.000Z","msg":"劍橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df73a70